This is an example static site built with the functor.systems Hakyll template.

= Features

- *Typst* for content authoring with full HTML export support
- *Hakyll* static site generator with Haskell configuration
- *Blaze-html* templating instead of traditional HTML templates
- *Tailwind CSS* for styling
- RSS, Atom, and JSON feeds automatically generated

= Getting Started

Edit the files in `root/` to add pages, and `posts/` to add blog posts. Configure site metadata in `src/Constants.hs`.
